
# 🏥 Vitalis – Doctor Appointment Booking Platform

Vitalis is a full-stack web application designed to simplify the process of booking and managing medical appointments. The platform connects patients, doctors, and administrators through a structured and role-based system, providing an efficient and user-friendly healthcare solution.

---

## ✨ Key Features

### 👤 Patient
- Account registration and login  
- Browse available doctors  
- Book and manage appointments  

### 🩺 Doctor
- Secure authentication  
- View scheduled appointments  
- Manage and update appointment status  

### 🛡️ Admin
- Manage doctor accounts and approvals  
- Monitor platform activity  
- Access a centralized dashboard for system control  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript  
- PHP  
- MySQL  
- XAMPP (Local Development Environment)  

---

## 🎯 Project Objective
The goal of this project is to design and develop a real-world full-stack application that demonstrates the integration of front-end and back-end technologies. It focuses on user authentication, role-based access control, and efficient data management.

---

## 📂 System Overview
Vitalis is structured around three main roles:
- **Patients**: interact with the system to book appointments  
- **Doctors**: manage their schedules and appointments  
- **Admin**: oversees and controls the entire platform  

